Former CIA director David Petraeus was sentenced to two years probation and fined $100,000 for leaking classified material to his mistress Paula Broadwell while she was writing his biography . 
  He had pleaded guilty to a misdemeanor count of unauthorized removal and retention of classified material . 
  Petraeus was wearing his wedding ring to the hearing in Charlotte, North Carolina on Thursday . 
  He told the court he was sorry for the ' pain my actions caused'